# Translation Pipeline Rules

- Use the mock `translate()` function only; do not call external LLM or translation APIs.
- Route document translation through `TranslationService`.
- Keep Excel, Word, and PDF parsing/writing logic in their format-specific modules.
- Prefer focused tests before behavior changes.
- Preserve supported document structure: Excel columns, Word bullets/tables/basic run formatting, and regenerated PDF text.
- Keep Lambda and worker code local-only. Do not require cloud credentials or deploy anything.
- Put scalability behavior in the service or worker layer: batching, caching, retries, throttling, and resumable jobs.
